metadata.name: Hello Mars!
metadata.description:
AstroKidz ventures to Planet Mars!

This 1 of 1 hand drawn piece is the first piece to be released in the AstroKidz Club collection.  

The AstroKidz Club Collection aims remind all human, future beyond-Earth explorers that "No Dream is Too Big".  This collection embraces diversity  and is rooted in space and climate education.
